beer.beer_description:
We make sure the gentle bitterness of this beer is rounded out with a classic malt flavour in true porter style.

To make things uniquely Feral (as we like to do), we add a subtle hickory flavour from German malts smoked over Beechwood which gives this porter a truly special and unexpected character.

It's flamin' sensational.
